 **Application Scenarios**: Mobile AI applications, edge computing\\n- **Related Technologies**: Knowledge distillation, model pruning, quantization techniques\\n\\n### 2. Natural Language Processing\\n- **Research Direction**: Multilingual models and cross-language understanding\\n- **Specific Problem**: How to build efficient multilingual NLP systems\\n- **Application Scenarios**: Global applications, multilingual customer service\\n- **Related Technologies**: Transformer, multi-task learning, transfer learning\\n\\n### 3. Computer Vision\\n- **Research Direction**: Few-shot learning and meta-learning\\n- **Specific Problem**: How to train effective vision models with scarce data\\n- **Application Scenarios**: Medical imaging, industrial inspection\\n- **Related Technologies**: Few-shot Learning, Meta-learning, data augmentation\\n\\n## Research Plan\\n\\n### Phase 1 (1-3 months)\\n- Literature review and survey\\n- Determine specific research questions\\n- Design experimental protocols\\n\\n### Phase 2 (4-6 months)\\n- Implement basic algorithms\\n- Conduct comparative experiments\\n- Analyze experimental results\\n\\n### Phase 3 (7-9 months)\\n- Optimize algorithm performance\\n- Write research papers\\n- Prepare for academic conferences\\n\\n### Phase 4 (10-12 months)\\n- Paper submission and revision\\n- Open source code release\\n- Technical blog writing\\n\\n## Expected Outcomes\\n- Publish 2-3 academic papers\\n- Open source 1-2 tool libraries\\n- Apply for 1-2 patents\\n- Establish research team\\n\\n## Collaboration Opportunities\\n- Find research partners in related fields\\n- Establish cooperation with industry\\n- Participate in international academic conferences\\n- Organize technical seminars\\n\\n---\\n/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_desktop_project_management_67580/music/music_collection.md:\\n# Music Collection Management\\n\\n## Collected Artists\\n\\n### Jay Chou (周杰伦)\\n- **Style**: Chinese Pop, R&B, Chinese Folk\\n- **Representative Works**: \\\"稻香\\\", \\\"青花瓷\\\", \\\"夜曲\\\"\\n- **Collected Albums**: 14 albums\\n- **Personal Rating**: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐\\n\\n### JJ Lin (林俊杰)\\n- **Style**: Chinese Pop, Ballad, Electronic\\n- **Representative Works**: \\\"江南\\\", \\\"一千年以后\\\", \\\"不为谁而作的歌\\\"\\n- **Collected Albums**: 12 albums\\n- **Personal Rating**: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐\\n\\n### Other Artists\\n- **Style**: Diverse\\n- **Collection Count**: 25 artists\\n- **Total Tracks**: 500+ songs\\n\\n## Music Classification\\n\\n### By Mood\\n- **Happy**: Light pop, electronic dance music\\n- **Relaxed**: Light music, classical music\\n- **Focused**: Pure music, ambient sounds\\n- **Exercise**: Strong rhythm, motivational music\\n\\n### By Language\\n- **Chinese**: 60%\\n- **English**: 25%\\n- **Japanese**: 10%\\n- **Others**: 5%\\n\\n## Collection Statistics\\n- **Total Tracks**: 1,250 songs\\n- **Total Duration**: About 75 hours\\n- **Collection Time**: 2018 to present\\n- **Update Frequency**: 2-3 new songs per week\\n\\n## Recommendation System\\nBased on personal preferences and listening history, recommend similar style music.\\n\\n---\\n/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_desktop_project_management_67580/play/game_plan/gaming_schedule.md:\\n# Gaming Plan and Schedule\\n\\n## Current Game List\\n\\n### Main Games\\n\\n1. **League of Legends**\\n\\n   - Game Type: MOBA\\n   - Current Rank: Gold\\n   - Target Rank: Platinum\\n   - Weekly Gaming Time: 10-15 hours\\n2. **Genshin Impact**\\n\\n   - Game Type: Open World RPG\\n   - Current Level: 60\\n   - Main Goals: Collect characters, explore world\\n   - Weekly Gaming Time: 5-8 hours\\n3. **Honor of Kings**\\n\\n   - Game Type: MOBA Mobile\\n   - Current Rank: Diamond\\n   - Target Rank: Star\\n   - Weekly Gaming Time: 3-5 hours\\n\\n## Gaming Time Schedule\\n\\n### Weekdays\\n\\n- **Evening**: 19:00-21:00 (2 hours)\\n- **Game Selection**: Choose 1-2 game