ivities**: ¥500\\n- **Other Entertainment**: ¥200\\n\\n### Annual Budget\\n- **Total**: ¥15,600\\n- **Average Monthly**: ¥1,300\\n\\n## Time Schedule\\n\\n### Weekdays\\n- **Evening**: 19:00-22:00 (3 hours)\\n- **Activities**: Watch movies, follow TV series, read\\n\\n### Weekends\\n- **Morning**: 10:00-12:00 (2 hours)\\n- **Afternoon**: 14:00-17:00 (3 hours)\\n- **Evening**: 19:00-22:00 (3 hours)\\n- **Activities**: Outdoor sports, friend gatherings, deep reading\\n\\n## Goals and Expectations\\n- Watch 4 new movies per month\\n- Complete 1 technical book per quarter\\n- Exercise 3 times per week\\n- Participate in 1 social activity per month\\n- Establish healthy entertainment-life balance\\n\\n---\\n/Users/REDACTED/workspace/geode/artifacts/eval/harnesses/mcpmark/.mcpmark_backups/backup_filesystem_desktop_project_management_67580/travel_plan/travel_bucket_list.md:\\n# Travel Bucket List\\n\\n## Domestic Travel Destinations\\n\\n### Completed ✅\\n1. **Beijing** (2023)\\n   - Forbidden City, Great Wall, Temple of Heaven\\n   - Hutong cultural experience\\n   - Beijing Roast Duck, Zhajiangmian\\n\\n2. **Shanghai** (2023)\\n   - The Bund night view, Oriental Pearl Tower\\n   - Yu Garden, Tianzifang\\n   - Xiaolongbao, Shengjianbao\\n\\n3. **Chengdu** (2022)\\n   - Giant Panda Base, Kuanzhai Alley\\n   - Dujiangyan, Mount Qingcheng\\n   - Hotpot, Chuanchuanxiang\\n\\n### Planned 📅\\n1. **Xi'an** (April 2024)\\n   - Terracotta Warriors, Big Wild Goose Pagoda\\n   - Muslim Street, Bell and Drum Towers\\n   - Roujiamo, Yangrou Paomo\\n   - Budget: ¥3,000\\n\\n2. **Hangzhou** (June 2024)\\n   - West Lake, Lingyin Temple\\n   - Xixi Wetland, Thousand Island Lake\\n   - Longjing Tea, Dongpo Pork\\n   - Budget: ¥2,500\\n\\n3. **Qingdao** (August 2024)\\n   - Zhanqiao Pier, Badaguan\\n   - Mount Lao, Beer Museum\\n   - Seafood, Beer\\n   - Budget: ¥2,800\\n\\n### Future Plans 🔮\\n1. **Tibet** (2025)\\n   - Potala Palace, Jokhang Temple\\n   - Nam Co Lake, Mount Everest Base C